<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Global Reach - Ningbo Dunfang Precision Machinery</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Serving clients worldwide with reliable logistics and dedicated customer support.">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo1.png" type="image/png">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
        
        :root {
            --primary: #9c8b7a;
            --primary-light: #d4c4b4;
            --primary-dark: #7a6a5a;
            --accent: #b8a898;
            --dark: #2a2a2a;
            --gray-dark: #5a5a5a;
            --gray: #8a8a8a;
            --gray-light: #b8b8b8;
            --bg-dark: #1a1a1a;
            --bg-cream: #faf9f7;
            --bg-warm: #f5f3f0;
            --bg-light: #ffffff;
            --border: #e8e6e3;
            --shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
        }
        
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--dark);
            background: var(--bg-cream);
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }
        
        .page-content { padding-top: 96px; }
        
        .advantage-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-warm) 0%, var(--bg-cream) 100%);
            padding: 6rem 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
        
        .hero-icon {
            width: 80px; height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(156, 139, 122, 0.3);
        }
        
        .hero-icon i { font-size: 2.5rem; color: white; }
        
        .hero-title {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--gray);
            max-width: 700px;
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        .content-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
        
        .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
        
        .section-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        }
        
        .section-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--gray);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        
        .content-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
        
        .content-card {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        
        .content-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px var(--shadow);
        }
        
        .content-card-icon {
            width: 56px; height: 56px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .content-card-icon i { font-size: 1.5rem; color: white; }
        
        .content-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .content-card p {
            color: var(--gray);
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        .image-gallery { margin: 4rem 0; }
        
        .gallery-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .gallery-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .gallery-item {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            aspect-ratio: 4/3;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .gallery-item img {
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        
        .gallery-item:hover img { transform: scale(1.1); }
        
        .gallery-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.8) 0%, transparent 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .gallery-overlay h4 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
        .gallery-overlay p { font-size: 0.875rem; opacity: 0.9; }
        
        .process-section {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            padding: 5rem 0;
            margin: 4rem 0;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        
        .process-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        
        .process-step { text-align: center; position: relative; }
        
        .process-step::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 30px; right: -50%;
            width: 100%; height: 2px;
            background: var(--border);
        }
        
        .process-step:last-child::after { display: none; }
        
        .process-number {
            width: 60px; height: 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .process-step h4 {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .process-step p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--gray); font-weight: 300; }
        
        .page-navigation {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 3rem 0;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            margin-top: 4rem;
        }
        
        .nav-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background: var(--bg-light);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: var(--dark);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        
        .nav-btn:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border-color: var(--primary);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(156, 139, 122, 0.2);
        }
        
        .nav-btn i { font-size: 1rem; }
        
        .back-home { background: var(--primary); color: white; border-color: var(--primary); }
        .back-home:hover { background: var(--primary-dark); border-color: var(--primary-dark); }
        
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .content-grid, .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
            .process-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
            .process-step::after { display: none; }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            .content-grid, .gallery-grid, .process-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .page-navigation { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
            .nav-btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--gray-light);
        }
        
        .footer-link {
            color: var(--gray-light);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .footer-link:hover {
            color: var(--primary-light);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar', {currentPage: 'home'}) %>

    <main class="page-content">
        <section class="advantage-hero">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 lg:px-12">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <div class="hero-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-globe-americas"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h1 class="hero-title">Global Reach</h1>
                    <p class="hero-subtitle">Serving clients worldwide with reliable logistics and dedicated customer support. Our international network ensures timely delivery and exceptional service across continents.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 lg:px-12 py-12">
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
                    <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Global Presence</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                            Dunfang has established a strong global presence with distribution networks across North America, Europe, Asia, and beyond. Our strategic logistics partnerships ensure timely deliveries to clients worldwide, regardless of location.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                            We offer a comprehensive range of shipping options, including ocean freight for cost-effective bulk deliveries and air logistics for urgent requirements. Our dedicated team handles all aspects of international shipping, including customs clearance and documentation.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                            With 24/7 multilingual customer support, we provide assistance across all time zones, ensuring that our clients receive prompt and effective service whenever they need it. Our global reach enables us to serve industries worldwide with consistent quality and reliability.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                        <div class="relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl" style="border-radius: 8px;">
                            <img src="/images/metal-images/Flashing Forming Tool.jpg" alt="Global Logistics" class="w-full object-cover" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<div class=\'image-placeholder h-96 rounded-xl\'><i class=\'fas fa-industry\'></i></div>'">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 lg:px-12">
            <div class="page-navigation">
                <a href="/" class="nav-btn back-home">
                    <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
                    Back to Why Choose Us
                </a>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
                    <a href="/advantage/quality" class="nav-btn">
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
                        Quality Assurance
                    </a>
                    <a href="/advantage/integration" class="nav-btn">
                        Integration
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
